text: A peaceful song from this game's upbeat soundtrack. I feel calm while listening to this one and find this picture reflects it pretty well. It's definitely the kind of theme I hear in my head when I play video games with my aligator and my bunny friend. We're always trying to beat our rivals, the bear with the jacket and the mysterious white thing with his helmet. Then there's always Mr.Potato with a spike on his head that tries to unplug our TV, he thinks we can't see him behind the grass.
